Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:06.67,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,"Nebude opakovat"?  To je každý léto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.79,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Blbec.
